    <introduction>
      <Value><![CDATA[<p>Queen Margaret University (QMU), Edinburgh is amongst the first of the higher education institutions in Scotland to launch a British Sign Language (BSL) Action Plan. QMU’s move to develop a supportive BSL-friendly culture for staff and students will contribute to Scotland’s ambition to become the best place in the world for BSL users to live, work and visit.</p>]]></Value>
